Name: CHEMEDEPRAmountQuantityUnitCode
Title: Amount Quantity Unit Codes
Description: Unit Codes for amount quantity units.  These are all unit codes about amount quantities, excluding time units.

Name: CHEMEDEPRPaperFormat
Title: Paper Formats
Description: Paper formats for generated original representations.

Name: CHEMEDEPRRouteOfAdministration
Title: Route of Administration
Description: Valueset RouteOfAdministration filtered for ambulatory care use.  This value set is a subset of the mandatory value set ([EDQM - RouteOfAdministration](http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-term/ValueSet/edqm-routeofadministration)) that contains only values compatible with ambulatory care. We recommend implementers to focus on supporting this value set instead of the complete one.

Name: CHEMEDEprActSubstanceAdminSubstitutionCode
Title: Substance Administration Substitution Codes
Description: Codes in use to allow or deny medication substitution.

Name: CHEMEDEPRTimeQuantityUnitCode
Title: Time Quantity Unit Codes
Description: Unit Codes for time quantity units.  These are all unit codes about time quantities, excluding amount units.
